s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/?p=17912\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:576:\"<p>Starting with the free version of WPtouch, it has always been important to us to provide our mobile solutions in as many languages as possible. The previous version of WPtouch Pro, version 2.0, launched with approximately 10 languages almost three years ago. During the development of WPtouch Pro 3.0 we decided to spend additional resources [...]</p><p>The post <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/05/wptouch-pro-21-languages-and-counting/\">WPtouch Pro: 21 Languages and Counting</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com\">BraveNewCode Inc.</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"Duane\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1761:\"<p>Starting with the free version of WPtouch, it has always been important to us to provide our mobile solutions in as many languages as possible. The previous version of WPtouch Pro, version 2.0, launched with approximately 10 languages almost three years ago.</p>\n<p>During the development of WPtouch Pro 3.0 we decided to spend additional resources adding some of the most often requested languages, including those that require a right-to-left orientation. We&#8217;re happy to announce that the new version of WPtouch Pro has been <strong><i>professionally translated</i></strong> into 21 different languages.</p>\n<p>Here is an exhaustive list of all the languages that WPtouch Pro currently ships with:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>English</li>\n<li>Spanish</li>\n<li>Portuguese</li>\n<li>French</li>\n<li>German</li>\n<li>Italian</li>\n<li>Japanese</li>\n<li>Arabic</li>\n<li>Hindi</li>\n<li>Korean</li>\n<li>Danish</li>\n<li>Russian</li>\n<li>Dutch</li>\n<li>Chinese (Simplified and Traditional)</li>\n<li>Thai</li>\n<li>Turkish</li>\n<li>Vietnamese</li>\n<li>Indonesian</li>\n<li>Greek</li>\n<li>Hungarian</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>More Languages Soon!</h3>\n<p>Our official Hebrew translation is nearly complete, and will also be included in one of our next few releases. We will continue building out language support into future versions, so please let us know if you are interested in a language that isn&#8217;t included in this list. Our customers are spread all over the world, and we&#8217;re excited to continue to expand the languages available in WPtouch Pro 3.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/05/wptouch-pro-21-languages-and-counting/\">WPtouch Pro: 21 Languages and Counting</a> appeared first on <a href=\"http://www.bravenewcode.com\">BraveNewCode Inc.</a>.</p>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"http://www.bravenewcode.com/2013/05/wptouch-pro-21-languages-and-counting/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"1\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7: